This is a JSON report produced by the application when it ingests and processes a CSV. To generate one to submit:

Go to your live app: https://splitfair-sooty.vercel.app/dashboard
Click Import CSV (or go to /import).
Upload a CSV file.
If there are anomalies, select the resolution options in the UI (e.g., map users, ignore duplicates) and click Commit Import.
Go to the dashboard, scroll down to the Import Jobs list, and click View Report for that job (or go to /import-report/<job-id>).
Copy the resulting JSON report of anomalies and resolutions.
